casebody.data:
Ellen S. Botsford v. Andrew J. Murphy. Jacob V. Rogers for the motion. Padgham da, Padgham against..

[See 47 Mich. 537.)

Costs — Charge for obtaining copy of record

Tlio charge for obtaining a copy of the record for the printer is a proper item in taxing costs in cases at law.

. Motion for retaxation of costs.

Submitted and denied April 18.
